('The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle.', 'The first steps of our fight against the Scourge go well. We have had some successes, and hopefully my assistance can aid you in bringing future success to the battle.', 12301, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 31882),
('The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle.', 'The battle goes well. The Scourge forces seem weakened. I believe it will only be a matter of time before we drive them from our shores. I will turn my magics to you, to aid in this struggle.', 12300, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 31882),
('The battle is won. For the time being, the Scourge threat has been pushed back. Our resources can be channeled into aiding you, in thanks and preparation for the future.', 'The battle is won. For the time being, the Scourge threat has been pushed back. Our resources can be channeled into aiding you, in thanks and preparation for the future.', 12299, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 2, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 31882),
