('The time has come for Horde and Alliance to look towards the north and the invasion of the Scourge. In recent days, territories across Kalimdor and the Eastern Kingdoms have come under attack. Will you take up arms to save your land from destruction at their hands?', '', 12109, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 25, 0, 0, 0, 0, 0, 31882),
