('$N! You\'ve returned just to talk to me? That\'s very thoughtful of you, and you look pretty sweet in that outfit, too!$B$BYou don\'t know how good it makes me feel to see you. It can get pretty lonely up here, what with most of these yahoos not being able to see me, and all. It\'s a great thing that you did for all of us, and I\'ll never forget it!$B$BThanks for dropping in and saying hi, and don\'t be such a stranger.', '', 11830, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 71, 1, 0, 0, 1000, 0, 31882),
