('Finally! Put some fingers in your ears, your brain mighta just grown five sizes and I\'m worried it might leak out.$B$BSo, the Dark Irons spared his life and took him prisoner. Their leader, some self-important, uppity fella named Thauris-something, took Ironfoe for himself. And that was the last I saw of ol\' Windsor... *hic* \'scuse me.\n', '', 5035, 0, 0, 0, 1, 0, 0, 5, 1, 33, 0, 0, 0, 31882),
